The chemical constituents in Anatrim work within the satiety center by releasing a chemical compound similar to glucose but much stronger. The hypothalamus in the brain receives this signal as an indication that enough food has been consumed and this in turn stunts the appetite. Most people have positive results taking 1 - 2 capsules an hour before each meal with a large glass of water.
